{"section": "3.21.4: Solving linear homogeneous recurrence relations.", "qid": 0, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   1)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   Consider a linear homogeneous recurrence relation whose characteristic equation is (x - 3)(x + 2) = 0.\nWhich expression characterizes the set of all solutions to the recurrence relation? The variables s and t can be any real numbers.\n  </div>\n </div>\n <fieldset>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember139\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"\ns\u00b73n + t\u00b7(-2)n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember138&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    s\u00b73\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    + t\u00b7(-2)\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember141\">\n   <input aria-label=\"s\u00b73n + t\u00b72n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember140&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    s\u00b73\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    + t\u00b72\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember143\">\n   <input aria-label=\"s\u00b7(-3)n + t\u00b72n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember142&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    s\u00b7(-3)\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    + t\u00b72\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n </fieldset>\n</div>\n", "choices": ["<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember139\">\n <input aria-label=\"\ns\u00b73n + t\u00b7(-2)n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember138&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  s\u00b73\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n  + t\u00b7(-2)\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember141\">\n <input aria-label=\"s\u00b73n + t\u00b72n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember140&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  s\u00b73\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n  + t\u00b72\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember143\">\n <input aria-label=\"s\u00b7(-3)n + t\u00b72n\n\" name=\"41\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember142&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  s\u00b7(-3)\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n  + t\u00b72\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n"], "answer": "s\u00b73n + t\u00b7(-2)n", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation correct\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Correct\n </p>\n The solutions to  the characteristic equation are x = 3 and x = -2. Therefore the solutions are a linear combination of 3\n <sup>\n  n\n </sup>\n and (-2)\n <sup>\n  n\n </sup>\n .\n</div>\n"}